        <abstract>
            <p>Asks DO to give enclosed [letter?] from John Scott to Hooker.</p> 
<p>JS’s work on orchid self-sterility; <hi rend="italic">Acropera</hi> has 371250 seeds in one capsule.</p> 
            <p>Wishes something could be done for Scott.</p>
